Locations.15:
The hut will be closed except for bathroom use, first aid and court controls.  
No spectators.  Players should arrive for matches at designated match time and leave the facility immediately after match play is completed.  
Masks are to be worn at all times except when on court.  Players are to wash their hands or use hand sanitizer before going on court and wipe down their equipment.  Players should maintain 6’ social distancing during change overs and breaks while on court.  Avoid physical contact on court such as shaking hands and high 5’s.  Avoid using your hands to pick up balls.
